    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit delivers linear power delivery through its individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains composed with a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential and a recently inspected rear subframe for structural integrity. Maintenance is up to date, including a comprehensive double VANOS service and shim-and-bucket valve adjustment within the last 15,000 miles. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are sharp, ensuring the signature M-division tactile feedback and communicative hydraulic steering rack are fully intact.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
