    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the ideal choice for a driver seeking a reliable, premium experience without the brand-new price tag. The exterior presents beautifully, with the paint retaining a deep luster, though a close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the heated seats to the premium sound system and navigation, is in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car has been treated with the utmost care, boasting a complete service history including recent fluid flushes and a fresh set of brake pads. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, ensuring you won't face immediate maintenance costs. This is a non-smoker's car that has been primarily garaged, offering a smooth, quiet ride that feels tight and responsive on the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
